name: KRyptoken
description: KRyptoken is a digital or virtual currency built to empower both the economy and the community by providing a sustainably remunerative business centric ecosystem based on the advantages of blockchain and the semantic web (3.0) framework. Perhaps the first all-Filipino asset created to serve all corners of the global crypto sphere, $KRYPT is committed to create, to innovate and to deliver effective enterprise solutions thru well-founded business models and the application of technology and relative performance indicators, subsequently maximizing revenue potential and overall profitability. KRYPT will propel the progressive build of KRYPToCommunity Ecosystem (KoC) as a utility, project, governance, DeFi and NFT.
